ayerprofile%5C%22%3EMark%20Boucher%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0opened%20up%20on%20Suryakumar%20Yadav's%20injury%20and%20said%20that%20the%20team%20management%20is%20currently%20waiting%20for%20updates%20from%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20awaiting%20updates%20on%20Suryakumar%20from%20the%20BCCI.%20We%20have%20always%20been%20under%20a%20cloud%20of%20fitness%20issues%20but%20we%20have%20a%20world-class%20medical%20team.%20We%20may%20lose%20one%20or%20two%20in%20terms%20of%20fitness%20but%20we%20have%20to%20move%20on%20as%20is%20sport%2C%26quot%3B%20Boucher%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20agency%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710853860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F6a4i7kq_suryakumar-yadav_625x300_10_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fbig-blow-for-mumbai-indians-suryakumar-yadav-to-miss-ipl-2024-opener-due-to-fitness-concerns-report-5269638%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Suryakumar%20Yadav%20is%20certain%20to%20miss%20Mumbai%20Indians'%20IPL%20opener%20against%20Gujarat%20Titans%20on%20March%2024%20as%20he%20is%20yet%20to%20get%20fitness%20clearance%20from%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy%20(NCA).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20Exercise%20Pill%20That%20Gives%20Benefits%20Of%20Working%20Out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExercise%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20boost%20your%20health%20and%20overall%20fitness%2C%20but%20what%20if%20a%20pill%20could%20offer%20the%20same%20benefits%20as%20a%20workout%3F%20It%20doesn't%20seem%20like%20a%20far-fetched%20idea.%20Researchers%20from%20the%20Washington%20University%20School%20of%20Medicine%20in%20St%20Louis%20have%20tested%20new%20drug%20compounds%20that%20appear%20to%20mimic%20the%20physical%20benefits%20of%20exercise%20in%20rodents.%20According%20to%20the%20researchers%2C%20a%20pill%20may%20someday%20be%20able%20to%20do%20the%20same%20in%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scientists%20say%20the%20pill%20could%20offer%20other%20benefits%20including%20making%20us%20feel%20younger%2C%20working%20against%20obesity%2C%20heart%20failure%2C%20and%20kidney%20decline%2C%20as%20well%20as%20staving%20off%20cognitive%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20were%20scheduled%20to%20present%20the%20findings%20on%20Monday%20at%20the%20spring%20meeting%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.acs.org%2Fpressroom%2Fpresspacs%2F2024%2Fmarch%2Fmimicking-exercise-with-a-pill.html%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Chemical%20Society%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ACS).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20replace%20exercise%3B%20exercise%20is%20important%20on%20all%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Bahaa%20Elgendy%2C%20the%20project's%20principal%20investigator%20ahead%20of%20his%20presentation.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20can%20exercise%2C%20I%20should%20go%20ahead%20and%20get%20the%20physical%20activity.%20But%20there%20are%20so%20many%20cases%20in%20which%20a%20substitute%20is%20needed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2Fwell%2F2024%2F03%2F18%2Fexercise-mimicking-pill%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFortune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Elgendy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20saying%20by%20any%20means%20or%20forms%20that%20people%20shouldn't%20exercise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20%5Bthe%20drug%5D%20hopefully%20will%20help%20people%20who%20cannot%20exercise.%20And%2C%20in%20other%20cases%2C%20it%20can%20complement%20exercise%20programs%20to%20give%20more%20benefits%20to%20patients%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOr%2C%20it%20can%20be%20combined%20with%20the%20new%20wave%20of%20drugs%3A%20anti-diabetic%20drugs%20and%20drugs%20that%20are%20used%20for%20obesity%20and%20weight%20loss.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20drug%20that%20can%20mimic%20these%20effects%20could%20offset%20the%20muscle%20atrophy%20and%20weakness%20that%20can%20occur%20as%20people%20age%20or%20are%20affected%20by%20cancer%2C%20certain%20genetic%20conditions%20or%20other%20reasons%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20carry%20out%20regular%20physical%20activity%2C%20ACS%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Elgendy%20and%20his%20team%20have%20spent%20about%20a%20decade%20developing%20a%20compound%20called%20SLU-PP%3D332%2C%20it%20activates%20a%20group%20of%20proteins%20called%20estrogen-related%20receptors-%20-ERRa%2C%20ERRb%2C%20and%20ERRy-%20which%20Elgendy%20says%20are%20%26quot%3Bresponsible%20for%20activating%20some%20of%20the%20most%20important%20metabolic%20pathways%20in%20tissues%20with%20high-energy%20demand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20then%20created%20new%2C%20patentable%20molecules%20to%20make%20them%20more%20safe%2C%20potent%20and%20efficacious%20than%20SLU-PP-332.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20new%20generations%20we%20developed%20that%20I'm%20going%20to%20talk%20about%20today%2C%20these%20are%20predicted%20to%20make%20it%20hopefully%20to%20the%20clinic%20one%20day%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Elgendy%20tells%20Fortune.%20%26quot%3BThe%20translation%20from%20animals%20to%20humans%20takes%20a%20long%20time.%20We%20need%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20more%20preclinical%20testing%2C%20which%20is%20vital%20to%20ensure%20safety.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710853620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fj3ghckhg_exercise-pill_625x300_19_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fan-exercise-pill-that-gives-benefits-of-working-out-5269675%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20scientists%20say%20the%20pill%20could%20offer%20other%20benefits%20including%20making%20us%20feel%20younger%20and%20working%20against%20obesity%2C%20heart%20failure%2C%20and%20kidney%20decline.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fan-exercise-pill-that-gives-benefits-of-working-out-5269675%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fan-exercise-pill-that-gives-benefits-of-working-out-5269675%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fan-exercise-pill-that-gives-benefits-of-working-out-5269675%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Bill%20Gates%20company%20is%20about%20to%20start%20building%20a%20nuclear%20power%20plant%20in%20Wyoming%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22TerraPower%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f98ad62417f97b87cd439f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20rendering%20of%20TerraPower's%20nuclear%20power%20plant%20design.%3Cp%3ETerraPower%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETerraPower%2C%20which%20Bill%20Gates%20founded%2C%20plans%20to%20build%20its%20first%20nuclear%20power%20plant%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECEO%20Chris%20Levesque%20told%20the%20Financial%20Times%20it%20wants%20to%20start%20work%20on%20a%20site%20in%20Wyoming%20in%20June.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETerraPower%20says%20its%20reactor%20design%20is%20cheaper%20because%20they're%20cooled%20by%20liquid%20sodium%2C%20not%20water.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20company%20cofounded%20by%20Bill%20Gates%20is%20about%20to%20start%20building%20next-generation%20nuclear%20power%20plants%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Levesque%2C%20CEO%20of%20TerraPower%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F418907d1-d497-439c-9800-eb814226ab71%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20his%20firm%20will%20start%20building%20at%20a%20site%20near%20a%20coal%20plant%20in%20Kemmerer%2C