ress%20in%20developing%20similar%20tech%20in%20the%20US%20has%20stalled%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzirp-end-of-cushy-big-tech-job-perks-mass-layoffs-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHigh%20interest%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20made%20it%20tougher%20for%20startups%20to%20draw%20in%20funding%2C%20while%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20and%20subsequent%20exclusion%20from%20financial%20markets%20has%20made%20it%20tougher%20for%20companies%20to%20get%20the%20uranium%20needed%20for%20their%20reactors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20TerraPower%20pushed%20back%20the%20launch%20of%20its%20flagship%20project%20by%20at%20least%20two%20years%2C%20which%20Levesque%20attributed%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20hitting%20supplies%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Frussia-war-in-ukraine-bill-gates-nuclear-startup-uranium-fuel-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-assay%2C%20low-enriched%20uranium%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20October%20last%20year%20TerraPower%20missed%20out%20on%20making%20the%20shortlisted%20for%20the%20next%20round%20of%20the%20UK%20government's%20competition%20for%20small%20nuclear%20plants.%20Rolls-Royce%20is%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20contenders%20with%20its%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rolls-royce-smr.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esmall%20modular%20reactor%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(SMR)%20designs%20and%20has%20already%20secured%20more%20than%20%C2%A3200m%20of%20government%20funding%20in%20Britain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-terrapower-nuclear-power-plants-energy-tech-science-wyoming-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710853503000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F