r%20point%2C%20I%20took%20my%20first%20plane%20ride%20when%20I%20was%201.%20And%20yet%2C%20here%20they%20were%20in%20elementary%20and%20middle%20school%2C%20taking%20their%20first%20plane%20ride.%20But%20we%20have%20three%20kids.%20When%20planning%20a%20vacation%2C%20budgeting%20our%20stay%2C%20our%20meals%2C%20and%20our%20activities%2C%20the%20last%20thing%20we%20can%20afford%20is%20five%20round-trip%20plane%20tickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20we're%20far%20from%20wealthy%2C%20this%20isn't%20because%20we're%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20We%20swing%20a%20family%20vacation%20every%20year%3B%20we%20just%20always%20drive%20to%20our%20destination.%20So%2C%20what%20made%20our%20vacation%20to%20the%20Outer%20Banks%20different%3F%20This%20time%2C%20we%20saved%20up%20for%20it%2C%20not%20with%20money%20but%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-rewards-credit-cards%5C%22%3Erewards%20credit%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAn%20introductory%20bonus%20covered%20one%20person's%20ticket%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20taking%20our%20time%20and%20being%20strategic%2C%20we%20amassed%20enough%20travel%20points%20to%20fly%20our%20family%20of%20five%20from%20Kansas%20City%2C%20Missouri%2C%20to%20Norfolk%2C%20Virginia%2C%20and%20back%20again%2C%20and%20we%20had%20points%20left%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20strategy%20was%20simple.%20First%2C%20we%20applied%20for%20a%20credit%20card%20that%20offered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-current-credit-card-signup-bonuses%5C%22%3Eintroductory%20bonus%20points%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20cover%20at%20least%20one%20person's%20round-trip%20ticket%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20was%20before%20we%20started%20earning.%20Before%20we%20started%20using%20the%20credit%20card%2C%20we%20agreed%20on%20a%20plan%20for%20using%20the%20points%20we%20would%20earn.%20From%20there%2C%20we%20paid%20for%20everything%20with%20that%20card.%20And%20I%20mean%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20still%20paid%20off%20our%20credit%20card%20from%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-checking-accounts%5C%22%3Echecking%20account%3C%2Fa%3Eevery%20month%2C%20but%20the%20initial%20expenses%20were%20always%20charged%20to%20our%20credit%20card%20first.%20Our%20utility%20bills%2C%20our%20gas%2C%20our%20groceries%2C%20Christmas%20presents%2C%20birthday%20gifts%2C%20home%20improvement%2C%20weekend%20hotel%20stays%2C%20and%20even%20a%20short%20family%20vacation%20to%20the%20Ozarks.%20By%20taking%20our%20time%20and%20earning%20every%20point%20we%20could%2C%20we%20earned%20enough%20points%20for%20our%20family%20to%20fly%20to%20Virginia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20saved%20by%20staying%20with%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20our%20savings%20didn't%20stop%20with%20credit%20card%20points.%20My%20husband's%20parents%20invited%20us%20to%20join%20them%20in%20the%20Outer%20Banks%20and%20generously%20paid%20for%20our%20accommodations%20while%20we%20were%20there.%20Between%20a%20free%20stay%20and%20free%20flights%2C%20and%20local%20friends%20who%20let%20us%20use%20their%20car%20%E2%80%94%20our%20epic%20nine-day%20vacation%20cost%20us%20only%20the%20price%20of%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20our%20situation%20was%20unique%20to%20us%2C%20it%20illustrates%20a%20creative%20way%20to%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20your%20travel%20points.%20Whether%20you%20have%20long-distance%20friends%20who%20would%20love%20to%20have%20you%20stay%2C%20relatives%20with%20timeshares%20they're%20happy%20to%20let%20you%20in%20on%2C%20or%2C%20like%20us%2C%20you%20have%20loved%20ones%20invite%20you%20to%20share%20their%20vacation%20rental%2C%20the%20opportunity%20for%20a%20free%20place%20to%20stay%20comes%20up%20much%20more%20frequently%20than%20the%20offer%20of%20free%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaving%20up%20your%20travel%20points%20in%20anticipation%20of%20these%20occasions%20will%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20you%20t