ared%20on%20Monday's%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Fepisode%2F4ALHqqgmclhgTSDI2CP6gG%3Fsi%3D99ea61de6acf4cdb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArmchair%20Expert%20with%20Dax%20Shepard%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20alongside%20McGregor%2C%20and%20recalled%20how%20he%20got%20a%20staph%20infection%20after%20cutting%20his%20hand%20during%20a%20fight%20scene%20where%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20broken%20glass%20on%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20fighting%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20fighting%20around%20tables%2C%20we're%20fighting%20around%20glass%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20breakaway%20glass%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGyllenhaal%20said%20he%20cut%20his%20hand%20while%20filming%20a%20scene%20where%20his%20character%20jumps%20over%20a%20bar%20as%20a%20truck%20crashes%20through%20a%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20get%20up%2C%20I'm%20supposed%20to%20have%20been%20a%20little%20bit%20out%20of%20it.%20I%20put%20my%20hand%20on%20the%20bar%2C%20fucking%20straight%20glass%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGyllenhaal%20carried%20on%20shooting%20despite%20cutting%20his%20hand%20on%20glass%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThey'd%20already%20reshot%20the%20scene%20several%20times%20before%20that%20take%20and%20because%20this%20one%20looked%20good%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20ruin%20it%20by%20bringing%20up%20his%20injured%20hand%2C%20so%20he%20carried%20on%20filming%2C%20Gyllenhaal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20'We're%20not%20doing%20it%20again.'%20I%20felt%20the%20glass%20going%20in%20my%20hand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20remember%20the%20feeling%20and%20went%2C%20'That's%20a%20lot%20of%20glass%2C'%20and%20I%20just%20finished%20the%20fucking%20take.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20whole%20arm%20swelled%20up.%20It%20ended%20up%20being%20staph%2C%26quot%3B%20Gyllenhaal%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CDC%2C%20staph%20infections%20can%20be%20deadly%20or%20caus