20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIADMK)%2C%20the%20BJP%20appears%20to%20have%20regained%20some%20ground%20by%20forging%20alliances%20with%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD)%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-pawars-faction-is-real-nationalist-congress-party-says-election-commission-5006314%5C%22%3ENationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-chief-minister-nitish-kumar-says-will-stay-permanently-with-nda-now-5020268%5C%22%3Ereturn%20of%20the%20JD(U)%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP).%20Additionally%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%20recognised%20by%20the%20EC%20as%20the%20true%20Sena%20is%20now%20in%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20fold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Congress%20campaign%20commenced%20on%20a%20rocky%20note%20with%20the%20defections%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20to%20the%20NDA%2C%20along%20with%20internal%20splits%20within%20the%20NCP%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20and%20delays%20in%20finalising%20seat-sharing%20agreements%20with%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20consolidated%20its%20position%20by%20securing%20seat-sharing%20agreements%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20gaining%20the%20support%20of%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20and%20forming%20a%20coalition%20with%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20in%20five%20states%2C%20excluding%20Punjab.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20question%20arises%3A%20which%20party%20is%20better%20prepared%20in%20terms%20of%20alliances%3F%20We've%20categorised%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20into%20five%20types%20based%20on%20the%20strength%20of%20party%20alliances%20in%202019%3A%20(i)%20similar%2C%20(ii)%20weaker%2C%20(iii)%20stronger%2C%20(iv)%20lost%20opportunities%2C%20and%20(v)%20standalone%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlliance%20Arithmetic%20In%20INDIA%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20have%20argued%20that%20today's%20INDIA%20(Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance)%20bloc%20is%20essentially%20the%20UPA%20(United%20Progressive%20Alliance)%20of%20yesteryears.%20However%2C%20this%20criticism%20is%20no%20longer%20valid.%20The%20Congress%20has%20retained%20alliances%20in%2098%20seats%2C%20which%20constitutes%2018%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20strength.%20These%20seats%20are%20primarily%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20the%20Northeastern%20States.%20The%20alliances%20have%20been%20in%20place%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20are%20considered%20settled.%20Hence%2C%20there%20is%20limited%20potential%20for%20growth%20from%20these%20agreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2028%20seats%20-%205%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20strength%20-%20the%20Congress%20has%20weaker%20alliances%2C%20particularly%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20(JD-S)%2C%20its%20erstwhile%20ally%2C%20has%20now%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Despite%20winning%20only%20one%20seat%20in%202019%2C%20Congress%20hopes%20for%20significant%20gains%20here%2C%20banking%20on%20the%20implementation%20of%20guarantees%20by%20its%20state%20government.%20However%2C%20the%20departure%20of%20the%20JD(S)%20could%20dent%20its%20prospects%2C%20especially%20in%20Southern%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20however%2C%20has%20a%20stronger%20alliance%20in%20180%20seats%20compared%20to%202019.%20These%20seats%20are%20in%20Delhi%20(AAP)%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(SP)%2C%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20(National%20Conference)%2C%20Maharashtra%20(Uddhav's%20faction%20of%20Shiv%20Sena)%2C%20Goa%2C%20Chandigarh%2C%20and%20Gujarat%20(AAP).%20With%20just%20two%20seats%20won%20in%202019%20here%2C%20the%20Congress%20may%20expect%20some%20gains%20in%20these%20areas%20with%20the%20new%20alliances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20there%20is%20a%20block%20of%2082%20seats%20spread%20across%20Bihar%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20However%2C%20the%20INDIA%20front%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20weak%20lot%20here%20as%20key%20erstwhile%20allies%20like%20the%20JD(U)%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20have%20left%20the%20grouping.%20When%20the%20JD(U)%20was%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20opinion%20polls%20had%20predicted%20substantial%20gains%20for%20the%20alliance%20in%20Bihar.%20A%20deal%20with%20the%20Trinamool%20could%20have%20led%20to%20some%20gains%20for%20the%20block%20in%20West%20Bengal%20based%20on%202019%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20in%20contest%20in%20155%20seats%20without%20major%20allies%2C%20which%20make%20up%2029%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20strength.%20It%20will%20be%20fighting%20alone%20in%20states%20like%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Odisha.%20In%20five%20states%2C%20it%20faces%20a%20bipolar%20battle%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20where%20regional%20parties%20play%20no%20significant%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDA's%20Strengths%20And%20Weaknesses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20maintains%20alliances%20similar%20to%20the%202019%20formations%20in%2079%20seats%2C%20which%20make%20up%2015%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20strength.%20These%20seats%20are%20primarily%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20the%20Northeastern%20States.%20There%20is%20limited%20potential%20for%20growth%20from%20these%20agreements.%20Potential%20losses%20could%20have%20occurred%20had%20JD(U)%20not%20rejoined%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2052%20seats%2C%20constituting%2010%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20strength%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20weaker%20alliances.%20These%20seats%20are%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20where%20the%20Akalis%20and%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20respectively%2C%20have%20exited%20the%20NDA.%20Although%20these%20exits%20may%20not%20significantly%20impact%20the%20BJP's%20standalone%20fortunes%20in%20these%20states%2C%20they%20do%20complicate%20the%20party's%20strategy%20to%20gain%20traction%20in%20southern%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20stitched%20up%20stronger%20alliances%20for%20181%20seats%20in%20comparison%20to%202019.%20These%20include%20constituencies%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20(TDP)%2C%20Karnataka%20(JD-S)%2C%20Maharashtra%20(NCP)%2C%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(RLD%20and%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20an%20opportunity%20to%20expand%20the%20NDA%20in%20Odisha%20and%20Telangana%2C%20but%20talks%20in%20that%20direction%20have%20not%20materialised.%20These%20states%20collectively%20account%20for%2038%20seats%2C%20which%20is%207%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20in%20193%20seats%2C%20which%20represent%2035%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20BJP%20lacks%20strong%20allies%20and%20will%20contest%20independently.%20These%20seats%20are%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Goa%2C%20Telangana%2C%20and%20Kerala.%20In%20most%20of%20these%20states%2C%20the%20party%20faces%20a%20bipolar%20contest%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20Votes%20Flow%20Seamlessly%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20parties%20have%20sealed%20alliances%20on%20roughly%20the%20same%20number%20of%20seats.%20The%20opportunity%20lost%2C%20however%2C%20is%20higher%20for%20the%20Congress%20(82%20seats)%20than%20the%20BJP%20(38%20seats).%20The%20BJP%20has%20comparatively%20weaker%20alliances%20in%20a%20higher%20number%20of%20seats%20than%20the%20Congress%20-%2052%20versus%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20alliance%2C%20a%20seamless%20transfer%20of%20votes%20is%20crucial.%20Often%2C%20the%20post-poll%20vote%20share%20of%20an%20alliance%20is%20lower%20than%20the%20combined%20pre-poll%20vote%20share%20of%20the%20individual%20parties%20due%20to%20leakages.%20It%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20many%20NCP%20supporters%20will%20side%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20or%20whether%20an%20AAP%20voter%20will%20back%20the%20Congress%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710850020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F0c9alq0o_image_640x480_10_November_23.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbjp-vs-congress-who-is-more-battle-ready-for-lok-sabha-polls-2024-5268896%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Both%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20have%20sealed%20alliances%20on%20roughly%20the%20same%20number%20of%20seats.%20The%20opportunity%20lost%2C%20however%2C%20is%20higher%20for%20the%20Congress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbjp-vs-congress-who-is-more-battle-ready-for-lok-sabha-polls-2024-5268896%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbjp-vs-congress-who-is-more-battle-ready-for-lok-sabha-polls-2024-5268896%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbjp-vs-congress-who-is-more-battle-ready-for-lok-sabha-polls-2024-5268896%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Rose%20Hanbury%20Said%20On%20Prince%20William%20Affair%20Rumours%20Amid%20Kate%20Mystery%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESpeculation%20surrounding%C2%A0Princess%20of%20Wales%20%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttp