had%20sex%20with%20the%20girl%20in%20the%20toilet%20of%20a%20restaurant%20during%20a%20meal%20out%20for%20Valentine's%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen's%20lawyers%20also%20said%20that%20Hebblewhite%20was%20the%20first%20person%20to%20kiss%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20offence%20came%20to%20light%20after%20the%20girl's%20family%20members%20seized%20her%20phone%20and%20found%20explicit%20messages%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guardian-series.co.uk%2Fnews%2F24193248.leytonstone-teacher-erin-hebblewhite-banned-sex-pupil%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEast%20London%20and%20West%20Essex%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charges%20against%20Hebblewhite%20are%20related%20to%20sexual%20activity%20with%20a%20girl%20aged%20between%2013%20and%2017%20and%20abusing%20her%20position%20of%20trust%2C%20with%20another%20charge%20being%20sexual%20activity%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20teenager.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20two%20charges%20were%20taking%20and%20possession%20of%20indecent%20photographs%20of%20a%20girl%20under%20the%20age%20of%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710847800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fisckndt8_uk-police_625x300_04_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-teacher-who-had-sexual-relationship-with-student-banned-for-life-5269033%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20was%20also%20told%20that%20the%20teacher%20first%20had%20sex%20with%20the%20girl%20in%20the%20toilet%20of%20a%20restaurant%20during%20a%20meal%20out%20for%20Valentine's%20Day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-teacher-who-had-sexual-relationship-with-student-banned-for-life-5269033%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-teacher-who-had-sexual-relationship-with-student-banned-for-life-5269033%2Famp