her.%20This%20coincides%20with%20the%20other%20bahu%20in%20the%20family%2C%20Hemant%20Soren's%20wife%20Kalpana%2C%20emerging%20as%20the%20party's%20voice%20as%20it%20gears%20up%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2031%2C%20amid%20speculation%20that%20Hemant%20Soren%20could%20make%20way%20for%20wife%20Kalpana%20to%20take%20over%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20if%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20moved%20to%20arrest%20him%2C%20his%20sister-in-law%20and%20three-time%20MLA%20Sita%20had%20said%20Kalpana%20has%20%26quot%3Bno%20political%20experience%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20later%2C%20Champai%20Soren%2C%20a%20trusted%20aide%20of%20the%20JMM%20first%20family%2C%20took%20over%20as%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister.%20A%20month%20later%2C%20the%20party%20chose%20Kalpana%20Soren%20to%20address%20the%20mega%20INDIA%20rally%20in%20Mumbai%20that%20marked%20the%20end%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20this%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20stage%20with%20heavyweight%20leaders%20such%20as%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20the%2048-year-old%20delivered%20a%20confident%20speech%2C%20urging%20voters%20to%20rise%20against%20a%20%26quot%3Bdictatorial%20power%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Maharashtra%2C%20people%20were%20bought%20to%20topple%20the%20government.%20But%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20MLAs%20of%20the%20alliance%20showed%20that%20power%20that%20it%20cannot%20shake%20our%20government.%20A%20conspiracy%20was%20hatched%20to%20put%20my%20husband%20in%20jail.%20In%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20many%20other%20names%20will%20come%20up.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20those%20dictatorial%20forces%2C%20INDIA%20will%20not%20bow%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20thanked%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%20starting%20his%20yatra%20from%20Manipur.%20%26quot%3BHe%20chose%20Manipur%20when%20it%20was%20burning.%20I%20am%20saying%20this%20as%20a%20tribal.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20there%20was%20no%20one%20to%20take%20note%20of%20Manipur.%20Even%20today%2C%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20government%20are%20silent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalpana%20Soren%2C%20who%20holds%20engineering%20and%20MBA%20degrees%2C%20had%20largely%20stayed%20away%20from%20political%20limelight%20before%20her%20husband%20Hemant%20Soren%20was%20arrested%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%20The%20former%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%20against%20him%20and%20has%20accused%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20at%20the%20Centre%20of%20political%20vendetta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20days%20before%20Hemant%20Soren's%20arrest%2C%20there%20was%20speculation%20that%20Kalpana%20Soren%20may%20take%20his%20place.%20But%20later%2C%20Champai%20Soren's%20name%20emerged.%20The%20BJP%20had%20then%20claimed%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20JMM%20legislators%20were%20against%20Kalpana%20Soren's%20elevation%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20arrest%2C%20Kalpana%20Soren%20started%20managing%20Hemant%20Soren's%20Twitter%20handle%20and%20articulating%20the%20party's%20position%20in%20public%20meetings.%20The%20party%2C%20it%20is%20evident%2C%20wants%20to%20play%20the%20public%20sympathy%20card%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls%20by%20making%20her%20the%20face%20of%20its%20campaign.%20The%20JMM%20is%20yet%20to%20name%20its%20candidates%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20and%20Kalpana%20Soren%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20probable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Sita%20Soren%20has%20pulled%20the%20plug.%20Two%20days%20after%20her%20sister-in-law's%20speech%20at%20the%20Mumbai%20rally%2C%20she%20quit%20as%20MLA%2C%20resigned%20from%20JMM%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20In%20her%20resignation%20letter%20addressed%20to%20party%20chief%20and%20her%20father-in-law%20Shibu%20Soren%2C%20she%20mentioned%20that%20her%20husband%20and%20Hemant%20Soren's%20elder%20brother%2C%20late%20Durga%20Soren%2C%20played%20an%20active%20role%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20statehood%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20since%20his%20death%2C%20she%20and%20her%20family%20had%20been%20neglected.%20%26quot%3BMembers%20of%20the%20party%20and%20the%20family%20distanced%20us%20and%20this%20has%20been%20very%20painful%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20JMM%20had%20changed%20and%20was%20now%20controlled%20by%20people%20whose%20values%20don't%20match%20with%20hers.%20She%20also%20alleged%20a%20conspiracy%20against%20her.%20%26quot%3BI%20served%20the%20party%20for%2014%20years%2C%20but%20to%20date%2C%20I%20have%20not%20received%20the%20respect%20that%20I%20should%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20three-time%20MLA%20from%20Jharkhand's%20Jama%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20after%20joining%20BJP%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20party%20gave%20me%20no%20portfolio%2C%20but%20I%20walked%20along.%20But%20this%20cannot%20go%20on.%20And%20I%20believe%20lotus%20will%20bloom%20on%20all%2014%20seats%20of%20Jharkhand.%20Despite%20being%20loyal%20to%20the%20party%2C%20I%20could%20not%20work%20freely.%26quot%3B%C2%A0Asked%20if%20she%20had%20raised%20her%20concerns%20with%20the%20JMM%20leadership%20and%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20raised%20it%20multiple%20times%2C%20but%20he%20would%20only%20give%20assurances%20and%20do%20nothing.%26quot%3B%C2%A0Sita%20Soren%20termed%20Champai%20Soren%2C%20the%20new%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Brubber%20stamp%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JMM%20has%20termed%20the%20big%20exit%20as%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%26quot%3B.%20Party%20leader%20Manoj%20Pandey%20said%20Sita%20Soren%20was%20considered%20an%20important%20member%20of%20the%20party.%20%26quot%3BThe%20kind%20of%20respect%20she%20has%20received%20from%20this%20party%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20she%20will%20get%20anywhere%20else.%20If%20she%20comes%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20people%20opposing%20us%2C%20she%20will%20sabotage%20herself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710847080000%2C%22visual%22%3A