20the%20upcoming%20elections.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20is%20running%20for%20a%20third%20five-year%20term%20against%20a%20host%20of%20opposition%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrowing%20obstacles%20to%20government%20criticism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Congress%20party%20officials%20will%20reportedly%20retain%20partial%20access%20to%20their%20frozen%20accounts%20until%20the%20dispute%20is%20resolved%2C%20the%20case%20was%20only%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20pattern%20of%20actions%20in%20which%20government%20critics%20have%20suffered%20financial%20repercussions%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20state%20authorities.%20Over%20the%20past%20several%20years%2C%20officials%20have%20issued%20a%20raft%20of%20allegations%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fpolitics%2Fnews%2Fmore-than-40-more-opposition-mps-including-shashi-tharoor-suspended-from-lok-sabha-report-11702970155166.html%5C%22%3Efinancial%20impropriety%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sought%20to%20raid%20or%20restrict%20the%20activities%20of%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20and%20human%20rights%20activists.%20Though%20some%20investigations%20may%20be%20legitimate%20anticorruption%20inquiries%2C%20many%20appear%20to%20be%20politicised.%20In%20effect%2C%20they%20raise%20the%20costs%20for%20criticism%20of%20the%20government%2C%20draining%20the%20resources%20of%20an%20already%20fragile%20civil%20society%20sector%20and%20undermining%20the%20diversity%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%20discourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20civil%20society%20organisations%20face%20significant%20operational%20barriers%2C%20including%20tight%20restrictions%20on%20foreign%20funding%20under%20the%20Foreign%20Contribution%20Regulation%20Act%20(FCRA).%20To%20fundraise%20internationally%2C%20nonprofits%20must%20be%20licensed%20under%20the%20act%2C%20which%20entails%20strict%20controls%20administered%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs.%20Authorities%20have%20invoked%20the%20FCRA%20to%20investigate%20prominent%20organizations%20that%20have%20reported%20critically%20on%20the%20government%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Famnesty-fcra-violations-cbi-files-supplementary-charge-sheet%2Farticle67657397.ece%5C%22%3EAmnesty%20International%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20halted%20its%20activities%20because%20of%20the%20probe.%20The%20International%20Commission%20of%20Jurists%20found%20that%20some%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj.org%2Findia-repressive-law-on-foreign-contributions-stifles-ngos-must-be-revised-or-scrapped%2F%5C%22%3E19%2C000%20FCRA%20licenses%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0were%20canceled%20between%202014%20and%202020%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20cancellations%20were%20imposed%20%E2%80%9Cselectively%20to%20silence%20critical%20voices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndividuals%20involved%20in%20civil%20society%20activism%20are%20not%20much%20safer.%20Prominent%20journalist%20Rana%20Ayyub%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vocal%20critics%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20nationalist%20agenda%2C%20has%20endured%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20legal%20and%20extralegal%20harassment%2C%20including%20a%20years-long%20money-laundering%20investigation%20over%20the%20alleged%20misappropriation%20of%20funds%20from%20a%20COVID-19%20relief%20effort.%20BJP%20critic%20Harsh%20Mander%2C%20formerly%20affiliated%20with%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20has%20seen%20his%20home%20raided%20and%20his%20nonprofit%20investigated%20over%20alleged%20FCRA%20violations%2C%20with%20fellow%20activists%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fvindictive-witch-hunt-over-250-condemn-raids-on-harsh-mander%5C%22%3Edenouncing%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20enforcement%20actions%20as%20politically%20motivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20sprawling%20censorship%20apparatus%20to%20limit%20information%20diversity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%202024%20elections%20will%20be%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%2C%20with%20over%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wionews.com%2Findia-news%2Fgeneral-elections-2024-9688-crore-people-registered-to-vote-for-polls-election-commission-688693%5C%22%3E986%20million%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0registered%20to%20vote.%20Hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20citizens%20will%20rely%20on%20the%20internet%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20candidates%20and%20party%20platforms.%20But%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20asserted%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreedomhouse.org%2Fcountry%2Findia%2Ffreedom-net%2F2023%5C%22%3Eincreasing%20authority%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0over%20online%20content%2C%20particularly%20under%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20it%20regularly%20forces%20social%20media%20companies%20to%20remove%20content%20that%20officials%20deem%20unlawful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20or%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20policies%20that%20they%20champion%20are%20the%20prime%20targets%20of%20this%20censorship%20apparatus.%20In%20the%20first%20two%20months%20of%202024%2C%20the%20websites%20and%20social%20media%20accounts%20and%20posts%20that%20Indian%20authorities%20sought%20to%20scrub%20from%20the%20internet%20included%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ea%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Funion-govt-uses-it-act-to-attack-press-freedom-asks-caravan-to-take-down-report%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECaravan%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Emagazine%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0alleging%20that%20Indian%20soldiers%20killed%20three%20civilians%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eover%20a%20dozen%20social%20media%20accounts%20linked%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1063714%2Famid-farmers-protests-over-a-dozen-social-media-accounts-withheld-in-india%5C%22%3Eleaders%20of%20a%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20called%20for%20a%20stronger%20social%20safety%20net%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ea%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20from%20the%20US-based%20Sikh%20Coalition%2C%20calling%20on%20President%20Joseph%20Biden%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sikhcoalition.org%2Fpress-release%2Fsikh-coalition-statement-on-notice-of-withholding-from-x-and-indian-government-censorship%2F%5C%22%3Eadvocate%20for%20the%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20the%20protesting%20farmers%3B%20and%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHindutva%20Watch%20and%20India%20Hate%20Lab%2C%20two%20websites%20dedicated%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F1%2F31%2Fhate-crime-tracker-hindutva-watch-blocked-in-india-ahead-of-national-vote%5C%22%3Etracking%20hate%20crimes%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20hate%20speech%20in%20India%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20affiliated%20social%20media%20accounts.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affected%20content%20ranged%20from%20independent%20civil%20society%20research%20that%20reflected%20unfavorably%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies%20to%20online%20civic%20mobilisation%20that%20sought%20to%20influence%20policy%20directly.%20Diverse%20and%20independent%20discussion%20of%20politics%2C%20the%20economy%2C%20and%20broader%20societal%20challenges%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20shaping%20voters%E2%80%99%20choices%20ahead%20of%20elections.%20Degrading%20access%20to%20such%20information%20fundamentally%20limits%20free%20decision-making%20and%20infringes%20on%20the%20exercise%20of%20citizens%E2%80%99%20most%20important%20political%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20uneven%20playing%20field%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20free%20and%20fair%20election%20requires%20an%20environment%20in%20which%20people%20can%20discuss%20politics%2C%20express%20their%20personal%20views%2C%20and%20access%20information%20about%20the%20government%20and%20opposition%20without%20fear%20of%20retribution.%20From%20politicised%20FCRA%20enforcement%20to%20partisan%20online%20censorship%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions%20have%20undermined%20these%20basic%20rights.%20They%20also%20underscore%20officials%E2%80%99%20willingness%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreedomhouse.org%2Freport%2Ffreedom-world%2F2024%2Fmounting-damage-flawed-elections-and-armed-conflict%23manipulating-elections-undermining-democracy%5C%22%3Edeploy%20state%20resources%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20influence%20the%20elections%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20officials%E2%80%94including%20the%20tax%20investigation%20authorities%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20and%20those%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20who%20are%20tasked%20with%20enforcing%20online%20content%20regulations%E2%80%94should%20ensure%20that%20law%20enforcement%20efforts%20do%20not%20harm%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20elections.%20Investigations%20into%20alleged%20FCRA%20irregularities%20should%20not%20be%20initiated%20for%20political%20purposes%2C%20whether%20to%20hinder%20opposition%20politicians%20or%20to%20limit%20the%20activities%20of%20a%20civil%20society%20group.%20Independent%20oversight%20is%20crucial%3A%20election%20authorities%20should%20vigorously%20apply%20the%20principles%20set%20out%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20140407100248%2Fhttp%3A%2Feci.nic.in%2Feci_main%2FMCC-ENGLISH_28022014.pdf%5C%22%3EModel%20Code%20of%20Conduct%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20takes%20effect%20when%20election%20dates%20are%20announced%20and%20calls%20on%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20not%20abuse%20%E2%80%9Cits%20official%20position%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20its%20election%20campaign.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20corrective%20measures%20alone%20will%20not%20guarantee%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%20Political%20leaders%20have%20employed%20even%20blunter%20instruments%20to%20silence%20dissent.%20Indian%20journalists%20are%20all%20too%20frequently%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreedomhouse.org%2Fcountry%2Findia%2Ffreedom-net%2F2023%5C%22%3Earrested%20or%20prosecuted%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20critical%20reporting%2C%20opposition%20politicians%20have%20been%20disqualified%20from%20running%20or%20barred%20from%20the%20legislature%2C%20and%20internet%20shutdowns%20remain%20common.%20However%2C%20a%20truly%20democratic%20process%20will%20be%20impossible%20if%20free%20expression%20is%20not%20protected%20from%20politicised%2C%20disproportionate%2C%20and%20illegitimate%20interference%20by%20government%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKian%20Vesteinsson%20is%20Senior%20Research%20Analyst%2C%20Technology%20and%20Democracy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreedomhouse.org%2Farticle%2Fahead-landmark-elections-indias-government-silences-dissent%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Freedom%20House%20website.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710846052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F04112925%2FVoting_machine_in_India.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fahead-of-landmark-elections-union-government-silences-dissent%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ruling%20party%20has%20deployed%20state%20regulators%20against%20its%20critics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fahead-of-landmark-elections-union-government-silences-dissent%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hong%20Kong%20passes%20tough%20security%20law%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710845749000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0E83%2Fproduction%2F_115651730_breaking-promo-976.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-68594448%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Authorities%20say%2