eath%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Salem%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20Salem%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20that%20V%20Ramesh%20worked%20day%20and%20night%20for%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20I%20am%20in%20Salem%2C%20I%20remember%20Auditor%20Ramesh...%20%3Cem%3EAaj%3C%2Fem%3E%20Salem%20%3Cem%3Eka%20mera%20vo%20Ramesh%20nahi%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Ramesh%20worked%20day%20and%20night%20for%20the%20party.%20He%20was%20a%20dedicated%20leader%20of%20our%20party.%20He%20was%20a%20great%20orator%20and%20a%20very%20hardworking%20man.%20I%20pay%20homage%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20state%20general%20secretary%20'auditor'%20V%20Ramesh%2C%2054%2C%20was%20hacked%20to%20death%20by%20an%20unknown%20gang%20inside%20the%20compound%20of%20his%20house%20in%20Maravaneri%20area%20in%20Salem%20town%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20remembered%20former%20Tamil%20Nadu%20BJP%20president%20KN%20Lakshmanan%20and%20said%20that%20his%20role%20in%20the%20anti-emergency%20movement%20was%20unforgettable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLakshmanan%20ji%20role%20in%20the%20anti-emergency%20movement%20and%20participation%20in%20socio-cultural%20activities%20will%20always%20be%20remembered.%20His%20contribution%20to%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state%20is%20unforgettable.%20He%20also%20started%20many%20schools%20in%20the%20state%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK%20N%20Lakshmanan%20passed%20away%20due%20to%20age%20related%20problems%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Sevvaipettai%20in%20Salem%20in%20June%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20said%20that%20his%20government%20had%20worked%20hard%20to%20ensure%20development%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20government%20is%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20ensure%20the%20development%20and%20prosperity%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20From%20free%20medical%20treatment%20to%20providing%20tap%20water%20connections%20in%20homes%2C%20from%20free%20ration%20facilities%20to%20benefiting%20women%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20through%20MUDRA%20Yojana%2C%20we%20have%20ensured%20to%20give%20the%20best%2C%20to%20serve%20the%20best%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20was%20also%20confident%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20would%20repose%20its%20faith%20in%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20decided%20that%20on%20April%2019%2C%20every%20vote%20will%20go%20to%20BJP%20and%20NDA.%20Now%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20decided%20-%20this%20time%20it%20will%20cross%20400%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20was%20also%20felicitated%20during%20his%20public%20meeting%20in%20Salem%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam-led%20Secular%20Progressive%20Alliance%2C%20which%20comprised%20INC%2C%20VCK%2C%20MDMK%2C%20CPI%2C%20CPI(M)%2C%20IUML%2C%20MMK%2C%20KMDK%2C%20TVK%2C%20AIFB%2C%20registered%20a%20landslide%20victory%20by%20winning%2038%20of%20the%2039%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20DMK%20won%2023%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20with%2033.2%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%2C%20Congress%20bagged%208%20seats%20with%2012.9%20per%20cent%20vote%20and%20CPI%20won%202%20seats%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20CPI(M)%20got%20a%20seat%2C%20IML%20won%201%20seat%20and%20independents%20were%20elected%20on%202%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PMK%2C%20a%20political%20party%20that%20mostly%20represents%20the%20Vanniyar%20minority%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20was%20the%20second%20main%20alliance%20partner%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%202019%2C%20which%20contested%20on%20seven%20alliance%20seats.%20With%20a%20vote%20percentage%20of%205.42%20per%20cent%2C%20it%20was%20unable%20to%20secure%20even%20one%20seat%20in%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PMK%20had%20a%20slight%20increase%20in%20vote%20share%20to%205.42%20per%20cent%20over%20seven%20seats%20in%202014%2C%20up%20from%204.4%20per%20cent%20for%20eight%20seats.%20Anbumani%20Ramadoss%20is%20currently%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20having%20being%20elected%20unopposed%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20will%20see%20voting%20on%20all%2039%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Phase%201%20on%20April%2019.%20Votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710841020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fik46hvr_pm-modi-salem-pti-1200_625x300_19_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-breaks-down-while-remembering-salems-ramesh-at-poll-rally-5268273%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP%20state%20general%20secretary%20'auditor'%20V%20Ramesh%2C%2054%2C%20was%20hacked%20to%20death%20by%20an%20unknown%20gang%20inside%20the%20compound%20of%20his%20house%20in%20Maravaneri%20area%20in%20Salem%20town%20in%202013.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-breaks-down-while-remembering-salems-ramesh-at-poll-rally-5268273%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-breaks-down-while-remembering-salems-ramesh-at-poll-rally-5268273%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-breaks-down-while-remembering-salems-ramesh-at-poll-rally-5268273%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20Electoral%20Bonds%3A%20CPI(M)%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Rule%20Out%20Moving%20SC%20Against%20SBI%2C%20Govt%20For%20Perjury%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F191