aud-in-mass-marriage-scheme-4993504%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChief%20Minister's%20Mass%20Marriage%20Scheme%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20woman%20married%20her%20own%20brother%20to%20avail%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20scheme%20when%20the%20groom%20she%20was%20to%20marry%20failed%20to%20show%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20during%20a%20mass%20wedding%20event%20at%20Maharajganj%20on%20March%205%2C%20the%20police%20said%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%2C%20Preeti%20Yadav%2C%20was%20persuaded%20by%20some%20middlemen%20to%20marry%20her%20brother%2C%20Krishna%2C%20when%20the%20groom%2C%20Ramesh%20Yadav%2C%20couldn't%20reach%20the%20venue%20on%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20was%20already%20married%20and%20had%20registered%20for%20the%20mass%20wedding%20scheme%20to%20score%20Rs%2051%2C000%20given%20to%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20probe%20was%20ordered%20and%20a%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20the%20siblings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20village%20development%20officer%20was%20also%20suspended%20and%20action%20is%20being%20taken%20against%20the%20official%20who%20verified%20their%20documents%20before%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20scheme%2C%20Rs%2051%2C000%20is%20given%20to%20couples%20getting%20married%3B%20Rs%2035%2C000%20is%20sent%20to%20the%20bride's%20bank%20account%20and%20Rs%2010%2C000%20is%20given%20for%20buying%20gifts%20for%20the%20couple%2C%20and%20Rs%206%2C000%20is%20marked%20for%20arranging%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20January%2C%20a%20similar%20fraud%20was%20reported%20in%20Ballia%20in%20which%20as%20many%20as%20240%20ineligible%20people%20enrolled%20themselves%20to%20derive%20these%20benefits.%20Twenty%20teams%20were%20formed%20and%20were%20sent%20from%20door%20to%20door%20to%20investigate%20the%20matter%20and%2015%20people%2C%20including%20some%20government%20officials%2C%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20had%20then%20decided%20to%20link%20the%20details%20of%20the%20newly-wed%20couples%20with%20Aadhaar%20to%20prevent%20such%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20will%20give%20marriage%20certificates%20to%20couples%20on%20the%20spot%20in%20the%20programme%20to%20stop%20the%20repeat%20of%20the%20fraud%2C%20state%20Social%20Welfare%20Minister%20Asim%20Arun%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20Dharmendra%20Kumar%20Gupta)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710839880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fohsflg0g_mass-marriage_625x300_19_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgroom-missing-up-woman-marries-brother-for-mass-wedding-scheme-benefits-5267916%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20yet%20another%20case%20of%20fraud%20related%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Mass%20Marriage%20Scheme%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20woman%20married%20her%20brother%20to%20avail%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20scheme%20when%20the%20groom%20she%20was%20to%20marry%20did%20not%20turn%20up%20to%20the%20event.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgroom-missing-up-woman-marries-brother-for-mass-wedding-scheme-benefits-5267916%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgroom-missing-up-woman-marries-brother-for-mass-wedding-scheme-benefits-5267916%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgroom-missing-up-woman-marries-brother-for-mass-wedding-scheme-benefits-5267916%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Messi%20fans%20to%20get%20refunds%20for%20no-show%20match%20in%20HK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710839720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1136%2Fproduction%2F_132960440_f9717293bd32217f