%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68603469%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68603469.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68603469.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assam%3A%20Government%20Reveals%20Religion-Wise%20Break-Up%20of%20NRC%20Exclusions%20for%20the%20First%20Time%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23221556%2F2022_11img23_Nov_2022_PTI11_23_2022_000240B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20the%20first%20time%20ever%2C%20the%20government%20has%20revealed%20details%20by%20religion%20from%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20or%20NRC%2C%20conducted%20under%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20published%20on%20August%2031%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%2C%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20said%20that%20of%20the%2016%20lakh%20names%20excluded%20from%20the%20final%20draft%20of%20NRC%2C%20there%20were%20seven%20lakh%20Muslims.%20He%20said%20there%20were%20five%20lakh%20Bengali%20Hindus%2C%20two%20lakh%20Assamese%20Hindus%20(caste%20Axomiya%20and%20Koch-Rajbongshi)%20and%201.5%20lakh%20Gorkhas%20on%20the%20list.%20He%20did%20not%20reveal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1065331%2F7-lakh-muslims-5-lakh-bengali-hindus-left-out-of-assam-nrc-says-cm-himanta-biswa-sarma%5C%22%3Ewho%20the%20remaining%203.5%20lakh%20persons%20were%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20has%20made%20claims%20on%20numbers%20that%20he%20thinks%20will%20apply%20for%20Indian%20citizenship%20under%20fresh%20rules%20issued%20for%20the%20contentious%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20recently.%20He%20is%20reported%20as%20telling%20News%20Live%2C%20a%20local%20TV%20channel%2C%20that%20only%20%E2%80%9C3%20to%206%20lakh%20people%20will%20apply%20with%20CAA%20and%20not%2020%2C%2018%20or%2015%20lakhs%20or%201.5%20crores%2C%20which%20some%20people%20are%20claiming.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECAA%20%E2%80%9Cfiasco%E2%80%9D%2C%20says%20Sarma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarma%20is%20battling%20growing%20resentment%20over%20CAA%20rules%20in%20Assam.%20Opposition%20and%20other%20civil%20society%20groups%20are%20annoyed%20over%20what%20they%20think%20would%20be%20an%20attack%20on%20indigenous%20culture%20of%20Assam%20if%20the%20law%20to%20fast-track%20citizenship%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpersecuted%E2%80%9D%20non-Muslim%20minorities%20from%C2%A0%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%20was%20to%20be%20implemented.%20The%20amended%20law%20was%20passed%20in%20December%202019%2C%20and%20led%20to%20severe%20protests%20and%20outrage%20in%20Assam%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarma%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20speculate%20that%20the%20Act%20would%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfiasco%E2%80%9D%20in%20Assam%2C%20and%20it%20would%20see%20the%20lowest%20numbers%20applying%20for%20Indian%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20opinion%2C%203%20to%206%20lakh%20people%20will%20apply%20with%20CAA%20and%20not%2020%2C%2018%20or%2015%20lakhs%20or%201.5%20crores%2C%20which%20some%20people%20are%20claiming.%20It%20can%20be%2010%25%20more%20or%20less%20but%20not%20more%20than%206%20lakhs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20cited%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fonly-3-6-lakh-people-may-apply-under-caa-in-assam-not-1-5-crore-himanta-biswa-sarma-101710777297588.html%5C%22%3Etelling%20the%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20CAA%20rules%20were%20announced%20last%20week%20and%20by%20April%2019%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20have%20around%2040%20days.%20This%20will%20be%20enough%20time%20to%20understand%20the%20actual%20scenario.%2013%20Hindu%20families%20in%20Gujarat%20have%20already%20been%20granted%20citizenship%20with%20CAA%20but%20in%20Assam%2C%20not%20many%20people%20have%20applied%20till%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20many%20families%2C%20especially%20Hindu%20Bengalis%2C%20entered%20Assam%20from%20Bangladesh%20after%20March%2025%2C%201971%2C%20the%20cut-off%20date%20for%20being%20entitled%20to%20get%20Indian%20citizenship%2C%20adding%20that%20some%20of%20them%20returned%20as%20well.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20these%20families%20were%20denied%20ration%20cards%20by%20the%20authorities%20at%20that%20time%2C%20so%20they%20only%20had%20one%20document%2C%20the%20refugee%20registration%20cards%20issued%20by%20border%20authorities.%20But%20Prateek%20Hajela%20(former%20state%20coordinator%20of%20NRC)%20didn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20these%20cards%20in%20the%20NRC%20updation%20process%2C%20due%20to%20this%2C%20many%20names%20were%20excluded%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20Sarma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Assam%20government%20went%20after%20Prateek%20Hajela%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20an%20IAS%20officer%20of%20the%20Assam-Meghalaya%20cadre%2C%20and%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fothers%2Fassam-cm-orders-probe-against-former-nrc-coordinator-prateek-hajela-for-alleged-irregularities-assam-nrc-prateekhajela-illegalimmigrants-probe-corruption-101681366646111.html%5C%22%3Eis%20set%20to%20face%20a%20probe%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20committed%20while%20updating%20the%20register%20that%20was%20aimed%20to%20detect%20undocumented%20persons%20who%20could%20be%20present%20in%20Assam.%20Hajela%20was%20appointed%20the%20NRC%20coordinator%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202019%20to%20oversee%20the%20entire%20exercise%20of%20the%20NRC.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710833451000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23221556%2F2022_11img23_Nov_2022_PT