pUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Famaya-muruzabal-mariano-chihade-red-queen-1235945149%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22So%20What%20Happens%20to%20the%20NRC%20and%20NPR%20Now%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F12171429%2Fwomen-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20can%20we%20expect%20a%20National%20Population%20Register%20(NPR)%20and%20a%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%3F%20That%20would%20depend%20on%20who%20in%20the%20government%20one%20believes.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20have%20a%20look%20at%20the%20real%20chronology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Shaheen%20Bagh%20protests%20began%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fmail-today%2Fstory%2Fwhy-pm-modi-chose-to-contradict-amit-shah-on-nrc-1630689-2019-12-23%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Delhi%20on%20December%2022%2C%202019%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20130%20crore%20people%20of%20India%20that%20ever%20since%20my%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%E2%80%A6from%20then%20until%20now%E2%80%A6there%20has%20been%20no%20discussion%20on%20the%20NRC%20anywhere%E2%80%A6%20we%20only%20had%20to%20implement%20it%20in%20Assam%20to%20follow%20Supreme%20Court%20directives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20claim%20went%20against%20the%20public%20statements%20made%20by%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20only%20days%20earlier.%20On%20December%2010%2C%20Shah%20told%20Parliament%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EIss%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Edesh%20mein%20%3C%2Fem%3ENRC%3Cem%3E%20hokar%20rahega%20%3C%2Fem%3E(there%20will%20definitely%20be%20an%20NRC%20in%20this%20nation)%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Emaan%20ke%20chaliye%3C%2Fem%3E%20NRC%20%3Cem%3Eaane%20wala%20hai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(you%20must%20assume%20that%20NRC%20is%20to%20come).%E2%80%9D%20At%20a%20rally%20in%20Jharkhand%20on%20December%203%2C%20he%20even%20set%20a%20deadline%20for%20the%20NRC%E2%80%99s%20completion%3A%202024.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20infiltrator%20will%20be%20identified%20and%20expelled%20before%20the%20next%20election%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20himself%20promised%20to%20bring%20the%20NRC%20in%20his%202019%20manifesto%3A%20%E2%80%98There%20has%20been%20a%20huge%20change%20in%20the%20cultural%20and%20linguistic%20identity%20of%20some%20areas%20due%20to%20illegal%20immigration%2C%20resulting%20in%20an%20adverse%20impact%20on%20local%20people%E2%80%99s%20livelihood%20and%20employment.%20We%20will%20expeditiously%20complete%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20process%20in%20these%20areas%20on%20priority.%20In%20the%20future%2C%20we%20will%20implement%20the%20NRC%20in%20a%20phased%20manner%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20no%20extradition%20treaty%20with%20Bangladesh%20or%20Pakistan.%20Assuming%20that%20the%20NPR%20and%20NRC%20locate%20undocumented%20migrants%2C%20the%20government%20has%20no%20means%20of%20sending%20them%20anywhere%20except%20to%20detention%2C%20as%20it%20was%20already%20doing%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20speech%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20took%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20the%20NRC.%20The%20Cabinet%20approved%20Rs%208%2C754%20crores%20for%20the%20Census%20to%20be%20conducted%20in%202021%20and%20Rs%203%2C941%20crores%20for%20%E2%80%9Cupdation%20of%20the%20National%20Population%20Register%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20the%20government%20underplayed%20the%20NPR%20move.%20It%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Canyone%E2%80%9D%2C%20including%20non-citizens%2C%20would%20be%20counted%20in%20the%20NPR%20for%20which%20%E2%80%9Cno%20proof%2C%20no%20document%2C%20no%20biometric%E2%80%9D%20was%20required%20because%2C%20according%20to%20the%20government%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20trust%20the%20public%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NPR%20exercise%20would%20begin%20in%20April%202020%20and%20end%20in%20September.%20COVID-19%20halted%20that.%20The%20NPR%2C%20the%20government%20claimed%2C%20would%20not%20be%20used%20for%20the%20NRC.%20Indeed%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20specifically%20stated%20the%20NPR%20had%20no%20relation%20to%20the%20NRC%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EIska%20dur%20dur%20tak%3C%2Fem%3E%20NRC%20%3Cem%3Ese%20kuchh%20bhi%20sambandh%20nahin%20hai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20even%20remotely%20connected%20to%20the%20NRC).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Flucknow-women-who-had-protested-against-caa-in-2020-put-under-house-arrest%5C%22%3ELucknow%3A%20Women%20Who%20Had%20Protested%20Against%20CAA%20in%202020%20Put%20Under%20%E2%80%98House%20Arrest%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CNPR%20is%20the%20database%20on%20which%20policy%20is%20made.%20NRC%20is%20a%20process%20in%20which%20people%20are%20asked%20to%20prove%20their%20citizenship.%20There%20is%20no%20connection%20between%20the%20two%20processes%2C%20nor%20can%20they%20be%20used%20in%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20survey.%20NPR%20data%20can%20never%20be%20used%20for%20NRC.%20Even%20the%20laws%20are%20different%E2%80%A6%20I%20assure%20people%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20minorities%2C%20that%20NPR%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20used%20for%20NRC.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20rumour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20rumour%20and%20the%20facts%20came%20out%20quite%20quickly.%20Twenty-two%20points%20of%20data%20would%20be%20collected%20in%20the%20NPR.%20The%20Modi%20government%20had%20added%20eight%20new%20ones.%20Details%20would%20be%20collected%20of%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20Aadhaar%2C%20passport%2C%20driving%20licence%2C%20mobile%20number%2C%20voter%20identity%20card%2C%20mother%20tongue%2C%20and%20the%20date%20and%20birthplace%20of%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20eight%20were%20not%20in%20the%202003%20Citizenship%20Rules%2C%20the%20legal%20framework%20for%20the%20NPR%2C%20and%20had%20been%20specifically%20added%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20some%20end.%20What%20was%20that%20end%3F%20When%20reporters%20pointed%20this%20out%20to%20then%20Union%20minister%20Prakash%20Javadekar%2C%20he%20said%20he%20had%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20seen%20the%20form%20finalised%20by%20experts%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearch%20into%20the%20laws%20and%20by-laws%20showed%20the%20NPR%20was%20not%20only%20linked%20to%20the%20NRC%2C%20it%20was%20its%20very%20foundation.%20The%20NPR%20list%20would%20be%20scanned%20by%20local%20officials%20going%20through%20it%20to%20mark%2C%20at%20their%20discretion%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdoubtful%20citizens%E2%80%9D.%20These%20individuals%20would%20then%20have%20to%20line%20up%20and%20prove%20their%20citizenship.%20Once%20the%20list%20was%20drawn%20up%20and%20put%20on%20display%2C%20anyone%20could%20complain%20or%20name%20an%20individual%20or%20a%20family%20as%20being%20%E2%80%9Cdoubtful%E2%80%9D%2C%20even%20anonymously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2024%2C%202019%2C%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20NPR%20was%20indeed%20the%20basis%20for%20NRC.%20Section%2014A%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%20empowered%20the%20government%20to%20compulsorily%20register%20every%20citizen%20of%20India%20and%20issue%20an%20identity%20card%20and%20to%20maintain%20a%20National%20Register%20of%20Indian%20Citizens.%20The%20citizenship%20register%20would%20be%20generated%20out%20of%20this%20NPR%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20someone%20dug%20up%20the%202018-19%20annual%20report%20of%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20home%20ministry%2C%20which%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20National%20Population%20Register%20is%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Indian%20Citizens%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%208%2C%202014%2C%20then%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20decided%20that%20NPR%20should%20be%20completed%20and%20taken%20to%20its%20logical%20conclusion%2C%20which%20is%20creation%20of%20a%20National%20Register%20of%20Indian%20Citizens%20by%20verification%20of%20citizenship%20status%20of%20every%20usual%20resident%20in%20the%20NPR.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2026%2C%202014%2C%20Rijiju%20told%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%3A%20%E2%80%98The%20NPR%20is%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20creation%20of%20a%20National%20Register%20of%20Indian%20Citizens%20by%20verifying%20the%20citizenship%20status%20of%20every%20usual%20resident.%E2%80%9D%20He%20made%20similar%20statements%20linking%20the%20NPR%20and%20NRC%20in%20parliament%20on%20July%2015%2C%2022%20and%2023%2C%202014%2C%20and%20on%20May%2013%2C%202015%20and%20November%2016%2C%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20is%20long%20gone.%20So%2C%20what%20is%20the%20actual%20status%20of%20the%20NPR%20and%20NRC%20after%20the%20CAA%20has%20arrived%3F%20We%20do%20not%20know%2C%20and%20that%20is%20concerning%20because%20it%20is%20a%20serious%20issue%20that%20has%20become%20clouded%20in%20doublespeak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAakar%20Patel%20is%20an%20author%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710832529000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F12171429%2Fwomen-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fso-what-happens-to-the-nrc-and-npr-now%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CAA%20is%20here.%20But%20what%20do%20we%20know%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government's%20plans%20with%20the%20National%20Population%20Register%20and%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fso-what-happens-to-the-nrc-and-npr-now%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alka%20Pande's%20New%20Set%20of%2014%20Collectible%20Books%20is%20an%20Ode%20to%20the%20Best%20of%20Indian%20Culture%20and%20Heritage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18172344%2Fimage-1978.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EEminent%20art%20historian%20and%20curator%20Alka%20Pande%E2%80%99s%20recent%20set%20of%2014%20collectible%20books%2C%20%3Ci%3E108%20Portraits%20of%20Indian%20Culture%20and%20Heritage%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20puts%20the%20spotlight%20on%2014%20disciplines%20ranging%20from%20art%2C%20architecture%2C%20objects%2C%20crafts%20and%20more.%20The%20immersive%20collection%20set%20is%20an%20encyclopedic%20work%20examining%20the%20development%20and%20history%20of%20Indian%20visual%20culture%20through%20various%20eras%20of%20history%20to%20the%20contemporary%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20set%20of%20books%20features%20a%20comprehensive%20historical%2C%20cultural%20and%20visual%20exploration%20of%20subjects%20ranging%20from%20objects%2C%20dance%2C%20food%2C%20architecture%2C%20printmaking%2C%20crafts%20and%20music%20to%20photography%2C%20sculpture%2C%20design%2C%20traditional%20art%2C%20textiles%2C%20modern%20and%20contemporary%20art%20and%20vernacular%20and%20indigenous%20art.%20Sprinkled%20with%20anecdotal%20personal%20stories%2C%20the%20subject%20of%20each%20book%20unfolds%20in%20a%20visual%20and%20textual%20story%20of%20108%20narratives.%20Each%20book%20comes%20with%20a%20takeaway%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20recipe%2C%20a%20masterclass%2C%20or%20an%20insightful%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20%3Ci%3E108%20Portraits%20of%20Indian%20Crafts%3C%2Fi%3E%20delves%20into%20the%20beauty%20of%20glazed%20pottery%20of%20the%20Indus%20Valley%20civilisation%20and%20takes%20readers%20through%20the%20craftsmanship%20of%20varied%20Indian%20states.%20It%20probes%20the%20designs%20of%20utilitarian%20objects%20and%20examines%20how%20they%20are%20both%20functional%20and%20pieces%20of%20aesthetic%20art.%20In%20%3Ci%3E108%20Portraits%20of%20Indian%20Food%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20Pande%20takes%20readers%20through%20a%20compelling%20journey%20of%20food%20in%20literature%20and%20painting%2C%20exploring%20the%20broader%20culture%20of%20food%20across%20the%20globe.%20She%20takes%20readers%20on%20a%20fascinating%20exploration%20of%20several%20costume%20styles%20in%20%3Ci%3E108%20Portraits%20of%20Indian%20Textiles%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ci%3E108%20Portraits%20of%20Indian%20Music%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20Pande%20traces%20a%20range%20of%20styles%2C%20including%20the%20contributions%20of%20Amir%20Khusro%20to%20Qawwali%2C%20Swami%20Haridas%20and%20Tansen%20to%20Dhrupad%2C%20ancient%20Sanskrit%20and%20Tamil%20treatises%2C%20Purandaradasa%20and%20the%20renowned%20%E2%80%98Trinity%E2%80%99%20to%20Carnatic%20music%2C%20Pandit%20Bhatkhande%E2%80%99s%20treatise%20on%20Hindustani%20classical%20music%2C%20and%20Rabindra%20Sangeet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBelow%20are%20excerpts%20from%20a%20conversation%20between%20Pande%20and%20Neha%20Kirpal.%20They%20have%20been%20lightly%20edited%20for%20style%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20was%20your%20idea%20and%20inspiration%20behind%20putting%20together%20your%20latest%20set%20of%2014%20collectible%20books%2C%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3E108%20Portraits%20of%20Indian%20Culture%20and%20Heritage%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20resulted%20from%20my%2030%20years%20of%20teaching%2C%20first%20in%20Punjab%20University%20and%20then%2010%20years%20at%20the%20College%20of%20Art%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20NIIFT%20Mohali%2C%20the%20DJ%20Academy%20of%20Design%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20and%20NID%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20realised%20after%20three%20decades%20of%20teaching%20was%20that%20most%20students%20were%20far%20removed%20from%20Indian%20aesthetics%20and%20philosophy.%20It%20was%20important%20for%20them%20to%20know%20and%20understand%20the%20traditional%20canons%20of%20Indian%20art.%20Only%20then%20could%20there%20be%20a%20complete%20understanding%20of%20traditional%20modern%20and%20contemporary%20Indian%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18160301%2Fimage-1975-300x168.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18160301%2Fimage-1975-300x168.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18160301%2Fimage-1975-1024x572.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18160301%2Fimage-1975.png%201086w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702200%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22168%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3Eby%20Dr%20Alka%20Pande%2C%20designer%20Ujan%20Dutta%20et%20al%20(Arthshila%20Trust)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20a%20unique%20ecosystem%20of%20visual%20arts%20and%20culture.%20And%20it%20is%20extremely%20important%20for%20our%20artists%2C%20and%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20Indian%20visual%20practice%2C%20to%20fully%20understand%20our%20significant%20and%20key%20traditional%20texts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20developed%20a%20set%20of%2014%20books%20across%2014%20disciplines%2C%20in%20which%20I%20felt%20confident%20enough%20to%20be%20a%20catalyst%20and%20a%20%3Cem%3Esutradhar%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20commentator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20books%20have%20comprehensive%20content%20deliberately%20written%20in%20a%20non-academic%20style.%20These%20books%20also%20provide%20a%20comprehensive%20reading%20list%20for%20those%20who%20wish%20to%20delve%20or%20probe%20deeper%20%5Binto%20the%20subjects%5D.%20Each%20book%20has%20a%20physical%20takeaway%20and%20provides%20an%20immersive%20aesthetic%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20books%20are%20like%20taste%20multipliers%20and%20will%20help%20enrich%20the%20palette%20and%20serving%20of%20the%20veritable%20moving%20feast%20which%20Indian%20culture%20and%20heritage%20has%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20was%20your%20process%20to%20pin%20down%20the%2014%20disciplines%20ranging%20from%20art%2C%20architecture%2C%20objects%2C%20crafts%2C%20photography%2C%20dance%2C%20objects%2C%20music%2C%20printmaking%2C%20food%2C%20sculptures%2C%20design%2C%20textiles%2C%20crafts%2C%20etc.%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20diversity%20and%20plural%20culture%20of%20India%20is%20represented%20through%20the%20uniqueness%20of%20the%20production%20of%20the%20most%20beautiful%20objects%2C%20buildings%20and%20crafts.%20All%20the%2014%20books%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20written%20represent%20the%20key%20aspects%20of%20the%20essence%20of%20what%20is%20Indian%20culture%20and%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20I%20took%20these%2014%20disciplines%20is%20because%20these%20come%20under%20the%20wide%20umbrella%20of%20art%20history.%20Since%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20trained%20art%20historian%20and%20have%20taught%20art%20history%20and%20aesthetics%20to%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20students%20from%20fashion%20designers%20to%20product%20designers%2C%20photographers%2C%20fine%20art%20students%20and%20artist%20historians%2C%20I%20felt%20comfortable%20enough%20to%20take%20the%20reader%20through%20my%20personal%20understanding%20of%20these%2014%20disciplines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20197px)%2085vw%2C%20197px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18171901%2Fimage-1976-197x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22197%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18171901%2Fimage-1976-197x300.png%20197w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18171901%2Fimage-1976.png%20462w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702216%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPotraits%20of%20Indian%20craft%20by%20Alka%20Pande%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20was%20quite%20simple.%20I%20began%20with%20a%20preface%20which%20was%20more%20like%20a%20preamble%20that%20lays%20down%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20book.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20sculpture%20book%20was%20important%20for%20me%20because%20my%20PhD%20was%20based%20around%20the%20manifestations%20of%20Shiva%2C%20with%20a%20special%20reference%20to%20sculptures.%20The%20topic%20of%20my%20research%20was%20based%20on%20the%20concept%20of%20Ardhanarishvara.%20I%20saw%20the%20numerous%20styles%20and%20disciplines%20of%20Indian%20sculpture%20from%20Indus%20Valley%20right%20up%20to%20the%20millennium%20statue.%20The%20materiality%2C%20stylistic%20influences%2C%20technical%20skill%2C%20and%20plasticity%20of%20sculpture%20%E2%80%93%20all%20contributed%20to%20my%20understanding%20of%20the%20art%20form.%20I%20also%20discussed%20my%20own%20journey%20with%20sculpture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20each%20book%20contains%20a%20detailed%20essay%20that%20discusses%20the%20history%20of%20that%20discipline.%20As%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20it%20spans%20from%20the%20Indus%20Valley%20bronze%20statuette%20to%20the%20millennium%20statue%2C%20covering%20the%20entire%20period%20from%20pre-modern%20to%20contemporary%20sculpture%2C%20including%20medieval%20and%20modern%20eras%2C%20up%20to%20the%20present%20times.%20One%20hundred%20and%20eight%20is%20a%20sacred%20number%20in%20Indian%20philosophy.%20I%20included%20108%20images%20with%20detailed%20captions%2C%20explaining%20the%20various%20aspects%20involved%20in%20the%20making%20of%20Indian%20sculpture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20book%2C%20I%20aim%20to%20provide%20an%20aesthetic%20experience.%20The%20book%20also%20has%20a%20takeaway%20and%20a%20reading%20list%20that%20will%20help%20the%20reader%20choose%20if%20he%20or%20she%20wants%20to%20go%20further%20or%20just%20be%20happy%20with%20understanding%20Indian%20sculpture%20in%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20this%20was%20my%20process%20%E2%80%93%20right%20from%20my%20own%20experiential%20journey%20to%20a%20more%20detailed%2C%20almost%20academic%2C%20essay%20to%20a%20more%20communicative%20format%20%E2%80%93%20because%20both%20images%20and%20text%20make%20an%20interesting%20story.%20Then%2C%20the%20relevance%20of%20108%2C%20and%20the%20immersive%20experience%20of%20a%20physical%20takeaway.%20Some%20books%20feature%20an%20immersive%20experience%20via%20a%20QR%20code%2C%20which%20links%20to%20either%20a%20website%20or%20a%20performance.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20Dance%20%5B%3Cem%3EPotraits%20of%20Indian%20Dance%20Forms%3C%2Fem%3E%5D.%20Finally%2C%20each%20book%20concludes%20with%20a%20detailed%20reading%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGive%20us%20an%20idea%20about%20the%20vast%20research%20of%20five%20years%20that%20went%20into%20its%20making.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five-year%20research%20was%20actually%20a%20gathering%20of%20all%20the%20information%2C%20i.e%2C%20my%20research%20over%20the%20last%2030%20years%20of%20my%20teaching.%20Five%20years%20went%20into%20the%20making%20%5Bof%20the%20books%5D.%20The%20research%20actually%20took%20much%20more%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20began%20from%20the%20time%20I%20pursued%20my%20MA%20and%20continued%20through%20my%20teaching%20career.%20Throughout%20this%20period%2C%20I%20engaged%20in%20continuous%20reading%20and%20upgrading%20of%20knowledge%20to%20enhance%20my%20understanding.%20The%20five%20years%20dedicated%20to%20research%20involved%20collecting%20and%20sifting%20through%20vast%20amounts%20of%20information%2C%20adding%20new%20insights%2C%20unpacking%20dense%20knowledge%2C%20and%20collecting%20suitable%20quotes%20from%20Sanskrit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20important%20in%20these%20five%20years%20was%20the%20specificity%20with%20which%20I%20looked%20at%20these%2014%20disciplines.%20I%20looked%20at%20these%20disciplines%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20Indian%20aesthetic.%20%5BThis%20is%5D%20because%20art%20history%20is%20a%20western%20implant%20into%20the%20Indian%20academic%20system%20of%20learning%20about%20art.%20We%2C%20in%20India%2C%20used%20to%20have%20what%20we%20call%20Saundariya%20Shastra%2C%20which%20is%20about%20the%20appreciation%20of%20beauty%2C%20and%20in%20pre-modern%20Indian%20academia%2C%20it%20all%20emerged%20from%20very%20specific%20canons%2C%20i.e.%2C%20from%20the%20Natya%20Shastra%2C%20the%20Chitrasutra%20embedded%20in%20the%20Vishnudharmottara%20Purana%2C%20Sanskrit%20poetry%20and%20literature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20traditional%20Indian%20art%2C%20we%20have%20canons%20for%20everything%20and%20these%20canons%20are%20well-documented%20but%20they%20are%20basically%20in%20Sanskrit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20unpacked%20a%20lot%20of%20those%20cannons%2C%20brought%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20information%20which%20was%20easier%20to%20access%2C%20and%20pulled%20it%20out%20from%20important%20translations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20in%20these%20five%20years%20%E2%80%93%20putting%20all%20my%20research%20of%2030%20years%20in%20a%20manner%20which%20is%20easier%20to%20communicate%20and%20packing%20it%20from%20the%20density%20of%20academia%20and%20making%20it%20more%20reader-friendly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETell%20our%20readers%20more%20about%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20number%20108%20in%20Indian%20art.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20significance%20of%20the%20number%20108%20is%20mentioned%20in%20every%20book.%20108%20represents%20the%20beads%20of%20the%20Akshar%20Mala%2C%20where%20we%20engage%20in%20Chintan%20and%20japas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20beads%20hold%20great%20importance%20for%20us%20as%20practising%20Sanatanis%20because%20Chintan%20or%20self-reflection%20is%20a%20very%20important%20aspect%20of%20Indian%20philosophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20this%20aspect%20that%20goes%20into%20the%20making%20of%20traditional%20art.%20Incorporating%20the%20spiritual%20dimension%20rather%20than%20the%20purely%20religious%20aspect%20was%C2%A0%20important%20for%20me.%20The%20Sri%20Yantra%2C%20which%20is%20an%20icon%20of%20Shiva%20Shakti%2C%20also%20has%20108%20power%20centres%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20193px)%2085vw%2C%20193px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18172503%2Fimage-1980-193x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22193%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18172503%2Fimage-1980-193x300.png%20193w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18172503%2Fimage-1980.png%20456w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPotraits%20of%20Indian%20music%20by%20Alka%20Pande%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20have%20your%20childhood%20impressions%20and%20exposures%20been%20pivotal%20in%20introducing%20you%20to%20the%20rich%20and%20myriad%20cultures%20of%20India%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20quite%20incredible%20how%20much%20impact%20one%E2%80%99s%20childhood%20can%20have%20on%20the%20development%20of%20our%20brain%20and%20inclination%20towards%20aesthetics.%20I%20was%20exposed%20to%20music%2C%20dance%20and%20the%20traditional%20way%20of%20living%20in%20my%20childhood.%20My%20grandfather%20was%20a%20scholar%20of%20Pali%2C%20and%20I%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20at%20his%20house%20in%20Meerut.%20My%20grandmother%20was%20very%20conversant%20with%20the%20traditional%20rituals%20of%20Kumaon.%20Since%20I%20am%20a%20Kumaoni%20Brahmin%2C%20I%20was%20also%20introduced%20to%20the%20rituals%20of%20Aipan%2C%20which%20were%20integral%20to%20our%20festivities.%20The%20Aipan%20or%20floor%20patterns%20are%20deeply%20symbolic%20and%20specific%20to%20each%20festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20different%20Aipans%20for%20weddings%2C%20sacred%20thread%20ceremonies%2C%20Holi%20and%20Diwali.%20Additionally%2C%20my%20grandmother%20would%20draw%20sacred%20icons%20of%20different%20gods%20and%20goddesses%20as%20part%20of%20our%20family%20festivities.%20I%20grew%20up%20witnessing%20the%20creation%20of%20these%20sacred%20icons%E2%80%99%20floor%20patterns%20and%20interior%20decorations%2C%20which%20were%20integral%20to%20traditional%20Indian%20households%20of%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20also%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20the%20rigour%20of%20traditional%20Indian%20classical%20music.%20My%20mother%2C%20a%20trained%20musician%20from%20the%20Gwalior%20gharana%2C%20would%20practice%20every%20morning%20from%205%3A30%20am%20to%207%20am%20throughout%20her%20life%20until%20her%20passing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20learnt%20Bharatanatyam%20from%20the%20legendary%20dancer%20Yamini%20Krishnamurthy.%20For%2010%20years%2C%20I%20was%20the%20music%20and%20dance%20critic%20for%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fi%3E%20in%20Chandigarh.%20I%20interacted%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20musicians%20%E2%80%93%20folk%20dancers%2C%20folk%20performers%2C%20classical%20dancers%2C%20classical%20musicians%20%E2%80%93%20and%20wrote%20about%20them.%20Then%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20curator%20dealing%20with%20contemporary%20Indian%20artists%2C%20meeting%20them%20and%20talking%20to%20them.%20All%20these%20things%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20my%20journey%20from%20my%20youth%20to%20the%20time%20I%20started%20writing%20books.%20They%20all%20came%20very%20handy%2C%20because%20the%20performing%20arts%20of%20India%20are%20actually%20what%20introduces%20you%20to%20the%20rich%20and%20deep%20symbolism%20in%20Indian%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESetting%20up%20the%20Kanha%20Museum%20of%20Art%20and%20Life%2C%20which%20was%20basically%20about%20Gond%20art%2C%20taught%20me%20a%20lot.%20I%20set%20up%20the%20Sculpture%20Gallery%20for%20the%20Udaipur%20City%20Palace%20that%20took%20me%20to%20another%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20it%20was%20%5Bdue%20t0%5D%20my%20own%20kind%20of%20interest%20because%20I%20wrote%20a%20book%20on%20the%20folk%20music%20and%20instruments%20of%20Punjab%2C%20which%20introduced%20me%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20plurality%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Sufi%20culture%2C%20Sikh%20culture%2C%20Hindu%20traditions%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20Gurmat%20Sangeet%20or%20Bhakti%20Sangeet%20of%20the%20Sikhs%20to%20the%20more%20secular%20songs%20of%20the%20Mirasis%20to%20the%20folk%20stories%20from%20rural%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20through%20the%20understanding%20of%20the%20performing%20arts%20of%20India%20that%20I%20learnt%20so%20much%20about%20the%20heritage%20and%20culture%2C%20because%20we%20see%20that%20even%20reflected%20in%20the%20architecture%20and%20buildings%2C%20dynamism%2C%20and%20interdisciplinary%20aspect%20of%20what%20makes%20Indian%20culture%20and%20heritage%20so%20unique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPlease%20share%20a%20few%20of%20your%20favourite%20personal%20anecdotes%20from%20the%20series.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20would%20say%20food%20and%20objects%20are%20two%20of%20my%20favourite%20books%20because%20there%E2%80%99s%20not%20so%20much%20documented%20in%20what%20you%20call%20Indian%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20194px)%2085vw%2C%20194px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18172024%2Fimage-1977-194x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22194%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18172024%2Fimage-1977-194x300.png%20194w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18172024%2Fimage-1977.png%20457w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702218%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPotraits%20of%20Indian%20food%20by%20Alka%20Pande%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20food%20is%20a%20variety%20of%20cuisines%2C%20ranging%20from%20the%20tribal%20cultures%2C%20the%20Adivasis%20as%20they%20were%20known%2C%20to%20folk%20and%20the%20hybridity%20of%20Indian%20cuisine.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20had%20so%20many%20people%20coming%20in%20and%20out%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20so%20there%20is%20influence%20from%20Central%20Asia%2C%20Persia%2C%20the%20Mughals%2C%20the%20Dutch%2C%20the%20Portuguese%2C%20the%20French%2C%20and%20the%20colonial%20era.%20Plus%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20regional%20influence.%20India%20itself%20has%20so%20many%20regional%20variations.%20Indian%20cuisine%20is%20incredible%3B%20there%20is%20no%20homogeneity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20of%20Indian%20food%20is%20in%20your%20kitchen.%20Every%20woman%20is%20an%20artist%20because%20of%20the%20way%20she%20creates%20a%20particular%20dish%2C%20and%20every%20household%20in%20India%2C%20probably%2C%20has%20their%20own%20way%20of%20creating%20or%20recreating%20a%20particular%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20were%20growing%20up%2C%20the%20snacks%20we%20got%20at%20tea%20time%20were%20mattris%20and%20besan%20laddoos%20%E2%80%93%20very%20different%20from%20the%20processed%20snacks%20being%20fed%20to%20children%20today.%20I%20used%20to%20watch%20my%20mother%20spending%20hours%20in%20the%20kitchen%20roasting%20the%20besan%20over%20slow%20fire%20and%20then%20making%20us%20all%20sit%20on%20the%20floor%20rolling%20out%20the%20laddoos.%20I%20had%20forgotten%20all%20this%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20After%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20death%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20remembered%20the%20laddoos%20as%20a%20gesture%20of%20affection%20and%20love%20for%20my%20mother.%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20keep%20her%20memory%20alive%20by%20making%20the%20same%20ladoos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20it%20has%20become%20a%20ritual%20for%20me.%20With%20the%20advent%20and%20close%20of%20winter%2C%20I%20make%20these%20laddoos%20annually%20and%20share%20them%20with%20friends%20and%20family%20in%20remembrance%20of%20the%20wonderful%20moments%20basking%20in%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPublished%20by%20Arthshila%20Trust%2C%20the%20paperback%20edition%20of%20each%20book%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20959%2C%20while%20a%20copy%20in%20hardcover%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%201%2C199.%20The%20set%20of%2014%20books%20in%20hardcover%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%2013%2C000%2C%20and%20the%20paperback%20set%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%2011%2C599.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENeha%20Kirpal%20is%20a%20freelance%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710832508000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18172344%2Fimage-1978.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Falka-pandes-new-set-of-14-collectible-books-is-an-ode-to-the-best-of-indian-culture-and-heritage%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Each%20book%20comes%20with%20a%20takeaway%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20recipe%2C%20a%20masterclass%2C%20or%20an%20insightful%20read.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Falka-pandes-new-set-of-14-collectible-books-is-an-ode-to-the-best-of-indian-culture-and-heritage%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Royal%20family%20removes%20individual%20bios%20of%20Prince%20Harry%20and%20wife%20Meghan%20Markle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710832364000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108609381%2Cimgsize-1306839.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Froyal-family-removes-individual-bios-of-prince-harry-and-wife-meghan-markle%2Farticleshow%2F108608602.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108608602.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPrince%20Harry%20and%20Meghan%20Markle's%20biographi