ass%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Cuisine%20connects%20us%20with%20the%20outside%20world%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFood%20is%20central%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20sense%20of%20identity%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344526%2Fsamvaad-tata-steel-foundation-celebrates-culture-of-tribes-of-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplays%20an%20integral%20role%20at%20Samvaad%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Every%20ingredient%2C%20be%20it%20vegetable%2C%20fruit%2C%20or%20spice%2C%20used%20in%20a%20dish%20represents%20a%20community%E2%80%99s%20biology%20and%20sociology%2C%20and%20forms%20a%20larger%20part%20of%20its%20historical%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20to%20chefs%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20India%20and%20even%20got%20an%20opportunity%20to%20relish%20some%20of%20their%20food%20at%20Gopal%20Maidan.%20Despite%20the%20difference%20in%20their%20preparation%20styles%20and%20ingredients%20used%2C%20something%20unified%20the%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Vasantha%20from%20the%20Irula%20tribe%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20said%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(finger%20millet)%20is%20the%20primary%20cereal%20in%20her%20village.%20They%20use%20it%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eballs.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Santi%20Bairak%20from%20the%20Chik%20Baraik%20tribe%20of%20Odisha%20uses%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20make%20fritters%2C%20%3Cem%3Esamosa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Emanchurian%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20even%20milkshakes.%20Then%20there%20is%20also%20Swati%20from%20the%20Oraon%20tribe%20who%20makes%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20cakes%20and%20pastries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20taste%20of%20their%20dishes%20%E2%80%94%20umami%2C%20spicy%20and%20sweet%20%E2%80%94%20are%20poles%20apart%2C%20the%20reason%20for%20using%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20the%20same%20%E2%80%94%20health%20benefits%20and%20easy%20access.%20And%20it%20got%20more%20interesting%20when%20Vasantha%20took%20a%20leaf%20out%20of%20Santi%E2%80%99s%20culinary%20book%2C%20went%20back%20home%2C%20and%20experimented%20with%20it!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Vasantha%2C%20Santi%20and%20other%20chefs%2C%20their%20role%20goes%20beyond%20cooking%20and%20showcasing%20their%20food%3B%20it%20is%20a%20way%20to%20connect%20their%20community%20with%20the%20outside%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFood%20is%20actually%20the%20easiest%20way%20to%20initiate%20a%20conversation%20with%20strangers.%20However%2C%20though%20people%20may%20connect%20via%20%3Cem%3EPunjabi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EGujarati%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20Goan%20cuisine%2C%20rarely%20are%20they%20aware%20of%20tribal%20cuisine.%20Part%20of%20the%20problem%20is%20the%20blanket%20labelling%20of%20tribal%20foods%20under%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98indigenous%E2%80%99%2C%20when%20in%20fact%20our%20food%20is%20as%20diverse%20as%20it%20can%20get.%20So%2C%20when%20people%20visit%20my%20stall%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20educate%20them%20about%20our%20tribe%E2%80%99s%20history%20and%20why%20we%20use%20certain%20ingredients%20the%20way%20we%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Palash%20Mallick%20from%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Lodha%20tribe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20happy%20that%20the%20sales%20of%20his%20star%20dish%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Edudh%20puli%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(rice%20dumplings)%20have%20increased%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20fried%20dumplings%20are%20made%20with%20rice%20flour%2C%20coconut%2C%20jaggery%20and%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20stalls%20away%2C%20Pritesh%20Kumar%20from%20the%20Oraon%20tribe%E2%80%99s%20Khalko%20clan%20excitedly%20narrated%20the%20fascinating%20story%20behind%20each%20dish%20while%20offering%20free%20samples.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Ebaas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(bamboo)%20pickle%20is%20good%20for%20your%20blood%2C%20and%20the%3Cem%3E%20demta%20chutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20made%20from%20red%20weaver%20ants%20is%20rich%20in%20protein%20and%20calcium.%20%3Cem%3EJamun%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%20helps%20control%20sugar%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20potential%20customer%20at%20his%20stall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20these%20chefs%20from%20the%20tribal%20community%2C%20their%20role%20goes%20beyond%20cooking%20and%20showcasing%20their%20food%3B%20it%20is%20a%20way%20to%20connect%20their%20community%20with%20the%20outside%20world.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-2048x1152.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344985%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20these%20home%20chefs%2C%20their%20role%20goes%20beyond%20cooking%20and%20showcasing%20their%20food%3B%20it%20is%20a%20way%20to%20connect%20their%20community%20with%20the%20outside%20world.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20cuisine%20helps%20uplift%20his%20community%2C%20Pritesh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20get%20to%20tell%20our%20stories%20through%20cuisine%20by%20shedding%20light%20on%20ingredients%2C%20preparation%20methods%2C%20taste%20and%20more.%20Get%20us%20more%20stalls%20like%20these.%20We%20will%20not%20only%20survive%20but%20also%20flourish.%20We%20offer%20foods%20that%20may%20not%20be%20available%20everywhere%20in%20India.%20Every%20generation%20closely%20guards%20these%20recipes.%20It%20is%20our%20fourth%20time%20here%20%5Bat%20the%20conclave%5D.%20Every%20year%2C%20we%20receive%20orders%20from%20across%20India%20once%20we%20go%20back%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMentioning%20the%20controversial%20plant%20of%20%3Cem%3Emahua%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3E(Madhuca%20longifolia)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMahua%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20unfortunately%20only%20popular%20as%20an%20alcoholic%20drink%20and%20hence%20people%20assume%20our%20community%20is%20backwards%20due%20to%20this.%20What%20many%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20is%20that%20%3Cem%3Emahua%3C%2Fem%3E%20can%20be%20used%20to%20make%20pickles%20and%20cookies%20as%20well.%20They%20have%20several%20health%20benefits.%20We%20aim%20to%20bring%20these%20dishes%20into%20the%20mainstream.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritesh%20and%20his%20family%20earn%20five%20months%E2%80%99%20worth%20of%20earnings%20within%20two%20days%20at%20Samvaad.%20He%20expressed%20hope%20that%20future%20generations%20will%20be%20eager%20to%20learn%20these%20recipes%20now%20due%20to%20its%20increasing%20market%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeeta%20Sandil%20of%20the%20Munda%20tribe%2C%20who%20was%20participating%20in%20the%20conclave%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%20said%20she%20had%20seen%20similar%20profits%20because%20of%20Samvaad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20we%20were%20the%20only%20ones%2C%20but%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20to%20see%20so%20many%20tribal%20communities.%20We%20sold%20a%20lot%20last%20year%2C%20so%20we%20are%20back%20with%20several%20new%20additions%20like%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20duck%20meat%2C%20%3Cem%3Edhuska%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Emasoor%20dal%20pakoda%3C%2Fem%3E%20(lentil%20fritters)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekhasi%20%3C%2Fem%3Epieces%20(goat%20legs).%20These%20dishes%20are%20good%20for%20bones%2C%20kidney%20stones%2C%20heart%20and%20gut.%20We%20prepare%20all%20the%20spices%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20the%20positive%20response%20here%2C%20Geeta%20expressed%20her%20desire%20to%20quit%20her%20restaurant%20job%20and%20start%20her%20own%20food%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamvaad%20is%20helping%20participants%20like%20Geeta%20who%20wish%20to%20walk%20on%20the%20entrepreneurial%20road.%20For%20instance%2C%20this%20year%2C%20it%20tied%20up%20with%20Zomato%20to%20home-deliver%20traditional%20cuisines%20prepared%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344574%2Ftata-samvaad-tribal-conclave-preserves-lost-heritage-artisans-sell-handicrafts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20the%20conclave%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20Jamshedpur%20for%20five%20days!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20not%20all%2C%20tribal%20cuisine%20has%20been%20taking%20over%20luxury%20dining%20tables%2C%20as%20TSF%20collaborated%20with%20Indian%20Hotels%20Company%20Limited%20(IHCL)%20to%20put%20up%20food%20carnivals%20and%20workshops%20at%20the%20Taj%20chain%20of%20hotels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%3A%20Gopi%20Karelia)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710506256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0960_11zon-1710505353-scaled.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344924%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tata%20Samvaad%2C%20a%20tribal%20conclave%20in%20Jamshedpur%20by%20the%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%2C%20showcased%20diverse%20indigenous%20cuisines%20from%2035%20tribes.%2